1
00:01:06,400 --> 00:01:07,680
I knew you'd be here.

2
00:01:13,320 --> 00:01:15,039
Did you come to ask me for the truth?

3
00:01:18,920 --> 00:01:19,680
I know.

4
00:01:20,480 --> 00:01:21,800
You never did such a thing.

5
00:01:24,080 --> 00:01:24,760
I came here

6
00:01:25,039 --> 00:01:25,720
just to tell you

7
00:01:27,320 --> 00:01:29,000
that even if no one else believes you,

8
00:01:29,600 --> 00:01:30,400
I do.

9
00:01:33,520 --> 00:01:33,960
But

10
00:01:34,800 --> 00:01:35,960
my belief doesn't matter.

11
00:01:38,240 --> 00:01:39,320
The industry right now

12
00:01:39,759 --> 00:01:40,680
doesn't need just my trust.

13
00:01:41,280 --> 00:01:42,720
It needs everyone's.

14
00:01:43,200 --> 00:01:44,360
Do you have any other way

15
00:01:44,880 --> 00:01:46,680
to prove you didn't do this?

16
00:02:00,400 --> 00:02:01,080
Do you know

17
00:02:03,080 --> 00:02:05,640
why I avoid same-sex themes so much?

18
00:02:06,520 --> 00:02:08,280
Why I acted so awkwardly in photos with you?

19
00:02:10,160 --> 00:02:11,360
It's not because I hate you.

20
00:02:13,320 --> 00:02:14,280
It's because

21
00:02:17,440 --> 00:02:18,320
I like men.

22
00:02:27,640 --> 00:02:28,560
This is the only way

23
00:02:28,560 --> 00:02:30,840
I can prove my innocence.

24
00:02:32,400 --> 00:02:33,760
But if I go public

25
00:02:33,760 --> 00:02:34,840
that I like men,

26
00:02:35,520 --> 00:02:37,079
it will only cause an even bigger storm.

27
00:02:39,640 --> 00:02:42,079
Some will say I'm using the topic to sell a persona.

28
00:02:43,040 --> 00:02:45,000
Some will say I'm chasing sensationalism on purpose.

29
00:02:45,920 --> 00:02:48,680
Others will dig up all my works

30
00:02:49,800 --> 00:02:51,240
and judge me frame by frame.

31
00:02:52,280 --> 00:02:53,040
This time,

32
00:02:56,600 --> 00:02:58,200
I'm a risk again.

33
00:02:59,360 --> 00:03:00,240
You're a risk.

34
00:03:02,520 --> 00:03:03,840
In this industry,

35
00:03:05,560 --> 00:03:06,280
sexual orientation,

36
00:03:07,880 --> 00:03:08,560
public opinion,

37
00:03:10,080 --> 00:03:10,760
capital,

38
00:03:11,800 --> 00:03:12,480
trust—

39
00:03:14,520 --> 00:03:15,720
all of these are more dangerous

40
00:03:15,920 --> 00:03:16,960
than acting.

41
00:03:18,920 --> 00:03:20,079
If I stay here,

42
00:03:20,280 --> 00:03:21,440
the crew will lose money.

43
00:03:22,280 --> 00:03:22,960
And you

44
00:03:25,720 --> 00:03:27,240
will be dragged into the storm too.

45
00:03:30,400 --> 00:03:31,800
I don't want to get you involved.

46
00:03:35,480 --> 00:03:36,880
What if I'm not afraid?

47
00:03:38,360 --> 00:03:39,600
Will you stay?

48
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:46,960
From now on,

49
00:03:47,800 --> 00:03:49,560
we'll face all the risks together.

50
00:03:53,120 --> 00:03:53,400
Don't

51
00:03:53,560 --> 00:03:54,640
turn me down.

52
00:03:58,360 --> 00:04:00,240
I'll face all of this with you.

53
00:04:08,040 --> 00:04:08,760
Let's go.

54
00:04:27,080 --> 00:04:27,800
I posted it.

55
00:04:29,000 --> 00:04:29,600
What did you post?

56
00:04:30,720 --> 00:04:31,360
A clarification.

57
00:04:43,200 --> 00:04:45,400
I have worked with Mr. Jian Mo for a long time.

58
00:04:45,680 --> 00:04:47,360
We are partners and friends.

59
00:04:48,080 --> 00:04:48,720
I believe

60
00:04:48,720 --> 00:04:49,920
in Mr. Jian Mo's character.

61
00:04:49,920 --> 00:04:51,400
He would never do such a thing.

62
00:04:51,880 --> 00:04:53,680
I hope everyone can see the truth clearly

63
00:04:53,880 --> 00:04:56,240
and give him innocence and fairness.

64
00:05:14,840 --> 00:05:15,880
Xinglang Xu

65
00:05:16,080 --> 00:05:17,480
Get rid of your Weibo

66
00:05:21,720 --> 00:05:22,560
The company

67
00:05:26,760 --> 00:05:27,760
