70
00:05:58,520 --> 00:05:59,159
Breakfast.

71
00:05:59,760 --> 00:06:00,920
Eat more protein.

72
00:06:01,760 --> 00:06:02,880
You've lost weight lately.

73
00:06:10,000 --> 00:06:11,880
Stop scrolling on your phone during breakfast.

74
00:06:15,560 --> 00:06:16,720
They're starting to attack you.

75
00:06:20,320 --> 00:06:20,760
I know.

76
00:06:23,440 --> 00:06:24,200
Actually,

77
00:06:25,680 --> 00:06:26,880
