88
00:06:59,640 --> 00:07:00,280
I got you involved.

89
00:07:01,240 --> 00:07:02,080
Enough of that.

90
00:07:02,960 --> 00:07:03,720
Just eat properly.

91
00:07:04,480 --> 00:07:05,440
Right now,

92
00:07:05,680 --> 00:07:06,520
