95
00:07:10,280 --> 00:07:10,800
Okay.

96
00:07:26,280 --> 00:07:27,160
You jinx!

97
00:07:27,840 --> 00:07:28,680
You ruined him!

98
00:07:29,040 --> 00:07:29,920
Why don't you just die?

99
00:07:31,800 --> 00:07:32,400
What's wrong?

100
00:07:33,520 --> 00:07:34,680
More messages from someone?

101
00:07:37,280 --> 00:07:37,760
Nothing.

102
00:07:39,240 --> 00:07:39,720
It's fine.

103
00:07:43,320 --> 00:07:44,360
After we finish eating,

104
00:07:44,680 --> 00:07:45,880
I'll take you somewhere fun.

105
00:07:48,760 --> 00:07:49,120
Okay.

106
00:07:51,120 --> 00:07:51,600
Jian Mo.

107
00:07:55,560 --> 00:07:55,880
Here.

108
00:07:56,440 --> 00:07:57,520
You hold the string, I'll hold the kite.

109
00:07:57,520 --> 00:07:58,159
When I say run,

110
00:07:58,159 --> 00:07:58,800
you start running.

111
00:07:59,000 --> 00:07:59,400
Got it?

112
00:07:59,560 --> 00:08:00,520
Are you sure the weather is good

113
00:08:00,600 --> 00:08:01,400
