114
00:08:02,640 --> 00:08:03,640
Why fly a kite?

115
00:08:04,120 --> 00:08:04,440
My grandpa said.

116
00:08:04,440 --> 00:08:05,080
My grandpa said,

117
00:08:05,280 --> 00:08:06,440
when people are troubled,

118
00:08:06,560 --> 00:08:07,520
just look at the sky.

119
00:08:08,520 --> 00:08:09,440
The sky is vast,

120
00:08:09,840 --> 00:08:10,920
and all worries fade away.

121
00:08:12,680 --> 00:08:13,320
I thought,

122
00:08:13,480 --> 00:08:15,000
