123
00:08:15,480 --> 00:08:16,400
Flying a kite kills two birds with one stone.

124
00:08:18,440 --> 00:08:19,800
Do you know how to fly a kite?

125
00:08:21,640 --> 00:08:22,440
Flying a kite?

126
00:08:23,320 --> 00:08:24,080
How hard can it be?

127
00:08:30,640 --> 00:08:31,160
Hurry!

128
00:08:31,320 --> 00:08:31,960
Run faster!

129
00:08:44,400 --> 00:08:45,400
You have to run against the wind.

130
00:08:46,480 --> 00:08:47,560
You're running with it right now.

131
00:08:50,440 --> 00:08:51,000
Run faster!

132
00:08:52,520 --> 00:08:53,040
Watch out!

133
00:09:02,280 --> 00:09:03,120
Are you watching the road

134
00:09:03,120 --> 00:09:04,080
or the kite?

135
00:09:04,840 --> 00:09:05,800
I can't keep up.

136
00:09:07,040 --> 00:09:08,520
Can't have both the road and the kite.

137
00:09:10,880 --> 00:09:11,320
Never mind.

138
00:09:11,920 --> 00:09:12,560
Face it

139
00:09:13,000 --> 00:09:14,480
