140
00:09:15,280 --> 00:09:15,840
C'mon.

141
00:09:16,080 --> 00:09:16,680
I'll buy you coffee.

142
00:09:16,960 --> 00:09:17,400
Let's go.

143
00:09:26,200 --> 00:09:26,720
Yep.

144
00:09:28,240 --> 00:09:29,000
This kind of relaxing way

145
00:09:29,760 --> 00:09:31,560
