146
00:09:31,720 --> 00:09:32,800
suits me better.

147
00:09:38,720 --> 00:09:39,200
Bro!

148
00:09:39,440 --> 00:09:41,320
Can we borrow your kite?

149
00:09:42,040 --> 00:09:42,680
Sure, go ahead.

150
00:09:43,760 --> 00:09:44,480
Let me tell you,

151
00:09:45,200 --> 00:09:46,360
