154
00:10:06,120 --> 00:10:06,920
Too easy.

155
00:10:07,360 --> 00:10:08,840
Only idiots can't fly it.

156
00:10:26,920 --> 00:10:28,120
Why did you want to be an actor?

157
00:10:31,400 --> 00:10:32,120
Before,

158
00:10:33,840 --> 00:10:35,200
I never planned to be an actor.

159
00:10:37,840 --> 00:10:39,680
I wanted to do so many different jobs.

160
00:10:41,360 --> 00:10:42,280
Watching James Bond,

161
00:10:43,280 --> 00:10:44,600
I wanted to be a spy.

162
00:10:45,600 --> 00:10:46,360
Watching Forrest Gump,

163
00:10:46,440 --> 00:10:47,480
I wanted to go running.

164
00:10:48,800 --> 00:10:50,240
After watching Interstellar,

165
00:10:51,800 --> 00:10:53,560
I wanted to be an astronaut.

166
00:10:55,400 --> 00:10:56,440
Then I realized,

167
00:10:58,720 --> 00:10:59,880
what I really wanted to be

168
00:11:01,520 --> 00:11:02,480
was an actor.

169
00:11:05,920 --> 00:11:07,120
To experience different lives,

170
00:11:08,400 --> 00:11:10,520
and show my feelings to the audience.

171
00:11:14,080 --> 00:11:14,600
What about you?

172
00:11:15,640 --> 00:11:16,840
Why did you want to be an actor?

173
00:11:17,200 --> 00:11:17,920
Because I'm handsome.

174
00:11:18,760 --> 00:11:19,480
A talent scout said

175
00:11:19,920 --> 00:11:21,080
I was born to be an actor.

176
00:11:23,520 --> 00:11:23,960
Really.

177
00:11:24,880 --> 00:11:25,400
At first

178
00:11:26,000 --> 00:11:27,160
I didn't want to be an actor either

179
00:11:28,520 --> 00:11:29,000
But later,

180
00:11:29,600 --> 00:11:31,440
after filming one drama after another

181
00:11:31,920 --> 00:11:32,720
I realized

182
00:11:33,560 --> 00:11:34,760
being an actor is awesome.

183
00:11:35,640 --> 00:11:37,160
You get to live different lives.

184
00:11:38,800 --> 00:11:39,600
So

185
00:11:40,600 --> 00:11:42,160
I don't want to play the same roles over and over.

186
00:11:44,160 --> 00:11:45,880
I want to explore more possibilities.

187
00:11:48,560 --> 00:11:49,360
Like a same-sex romance.

188
00:11:51,520 --> 00:11:52,080
Exactly.

189
00:11:55,680 --> 00:11:56,320
I think

190
00:11:57,720 --> 00:11:58,840
I'm really happy filming this drama.

191
00:12:04,960 --> 00:12:05,720
Acting with you,

192
00:12:08,440 --> 00:12:09,320
I really enjoy it.

193
00:12:11,040 --> 00:12:11,720
What about you?

194
00:12:27,920 --> 00:12:28,280
Bro!

195
00:12:28,440 --> 00:12:29,240
The kite is gone!

196
00:12:29,240 --> 00:12:31,480
Can you get it back for us?

197
00:12:32,320 --> 00:12:33,040
Go bother someone else!

198
00:12:33,680 --> 00:12:34,480
Don't worry.

199
00:12:34,840 --> 00:12:35,760
I'll go find it for you.

200
00:12:45,840 --> 00:12:47,120
You're Jian Mo.

201
00:12:53,800 --> 00:12:54,920
I'd know you anywhere.

202
00:12:55,200 --> 00:12:56,520
You are Jian Mo.

203
00:12:57,680 --> 00:12:58,600
What do you want?

204
00:12:59,400 --> 00:13:01,040
You're the one dragging our Xinglang down!

205
00:13:01,040 --> 00:13:01,840
Do you have any idea?

206
00:13:02,240 --> 00:13:03,600
He's a rising actor,

207
00:13:03,720 --> 00:13:05,600
