210
00:13:09,360 --> 00:13:10,280
I never sexually harassed anyone.

211
00:13:11,640 --> 00:13:13,120
I don't care if it's fake or not.

212
00:13:13,480 --> 00:13:14,880
All I care about is that he's losing followers,

213
00:13:14,880 --> 00:13:15,600
losing endorsements,

214
00:13:15,600 --> 00:13:16,760
losing his position—

215
00:13:16,960 --> 00:13:18,120
and it's all your fault.

216
00:13:18,520 --> 00:13:20,840
People like you should quit the industry.

217
00:13:21,280 --> 00:13:23,040
Never go near Xinglang again.

218
00:13:23,880 --> 00:13:25,120
What exactly do you want?

219
00:13:25,800 --> 00:13:26,720
I want to ruin you

220
00:13:27,120 --> 00:13:29,400
completely.

221
00:13:29,840 --> 00:13:31,640
Never let you affect Xinglang again.

222
00:13:34,760 --> 00:13:35,480
Help!

223
00:13:35,920 --> 00:13:36,600
Someone help!

224
00:13:36,600 --> 00:13:37,680
Jian Mo is harassing someone!

225
00:13:37,760 --> 00:13:38,880
He's harassing someone!

226
00:13:39,040 --> 00:13:41,200
Help! Jian Mo is harassing someone!

227
00:13:41,600 --> 00:13:42,960
Jian Mo is harassing someone!

228
00:13:43,720 --> 00:13:44,480
Let go of me!

229
00:13:47,640 --> 00:13:49,000
I recorded everything you just said

230
00:13:49,000 --> 00:13:50,720
on my phone.

231
00:13:51,040 --> 00:13:52,320
You sure you still want to make a scene?

232
00:13:53,520 --> 00:13:54,120
You

233
00:13:54,440 --> 00:13:55,960
He'll get you killed sooner or later.

234
00:14:00,080 --> 00:14:00,840
With fans like these,

235
00:14:01,600 --> 00:14:02,800
I can't even tell

236
00:14:03,880 --> 00:14:05,240
if they really like me

237
00:14:06,120 --> 00:14:08,280
or just the perfect version of me in their heads.

238
00:14:11,920 --> 00:14:12,840
What are you thinking about?

239
00:14:16,560 --> 00:14:17,280
Nothing.

240
00:14:18,920 --> 00:14:19,720
I was just wondering

241
00:14:21,280 --> 00:14:22,720
if, like she said,

242
00:14:24,560 --> 00:14:25,600
I'm the one who hurt you.

243
00:14:28,560 --> 00:14:29,640
Of course not.

244
00:14:30,000 --> 00:14:30,760
You're overthinking it.

245
00:14:39,040 --> 00:14:40,040
Insulting messages?

246
00:14:41,200 --> 00:14:41,840
No.

247
00:14:55,960 --> 00:14:56,920
I agree to meet.

248
00:14:57,280 --> 00:14:58,040
Where?

249
00:15:21,560 --> 00:15:22,880
Why did you come to find me?

250
00:15:23,440 --> 00:15:24,160
Mr. Jian Mo,

251
00:15:25,200 --> 00:15:25,920
there are things

252
00:15:26,600 --> 00:15:28,000
we have to discuss with you.

253
00:15:29,760 --> 00:15:31,280
Xu Xinglang was way too reckless this time.

254
00:15:31,760 --> 00:15:33,280
The company is very unhappy with him.

255
00:15:36,120 --> 00:15:36,960
Show him the contract.

256
00:15:40,320 --> 00:15:41,120
This is the contract

257
00:15:41,120 --> 00:15:42,320
the company prepared for Xinglang.

258
00:15:43,200 --> 00:15:44,040
You need to know first

259
00:15:44,440 --> 00:15:45,560
what he stands to lose.

260
00:15:45,760 --> 00:15:47,120
Then you can decide what to do.

261
00:15:51,080 --> 00:15:52,200
Targeting Xu Xinglang

262
00:15:52,560 --> 00:15:53,640
We have two plans.

263
00:15:54,240 --> 00:15:54,800
First,

264
00:15:55,360 --> 00:15:56,520
