272
00:16:09,480 --> 00:16:11,400
And you two will never have contact again.

273
00:16:12,200 --> 00:16:13,600
Your problems have nothing to do with him.

274
00:16:14,440 --> 00:16:15,400
We will give him

275
00:16:15,400 --> 00:16:16,360
