278
00:16:19,600 --> 00:16:20,320
No problem.

279
00:16:21,000 --> 00:16:22,520
The company has plenty of resources for him.

280
00:16:24,800 --> 00:16:25,280
Li Fang.

281
00:16:27,280 --> 00:16:27,800
You also want

282
00:16:27,800 --> 00:16:29,120
him to accept this contract, right?

283
00:16:30,960 --> 00:16:33,200
All these projects and terms

284
00:16:33,200 --> 00:16:34,680
the company has prepared for him

285
00:16:35,480 --> 00:16:36,600
are exactly what we've been fighting for

286
00:16:36,600 --> 00:16:37,840
but never got before.

287
00:16:40,280 --> 00:16:41,800
You know his talent and potential.

288
00:16:42,200 --> 00:16:43,120
This is more than enough

289
00:16:43,120 --> 00:16:44,280
for him to achieve his dreams.

290
00:16:45,440 --> 00:16:45,880
But

291
00:16:46,360 --> 00:16:47,680
if he keeps speaking up for you,

292
00:16:48,560 --> 00:16:49,200
then

293
00:16:50,360 --> 00:16:51,960
it won't just be you who loses your future.

294
00:16:52,920 --> 00:16:53,640
Li Fang.

295
00:16:54,880 --> 00:16:56,120
You'll take good care of him,

296
00:16:56,680 --> 00:16:57,320
won't you?

297
00:16:58,560 --> 00:17:00,000
I will definitely take good care of him for you.

298
00:17:00,760 --> 00:17:01,520
He will become

299
00:17:01,680 --> 00:17:03,040
a great actor.

300
00:17:06,040 --> 00:17:06,480
By the way,

301
00:17:08,000 --> 00:17:08,760
the contract says

302
00:17:09,480 --> 00:17:11,000
if we never contact each other again,

303
00:17:11,720 --> 00:17:12,880
he will get

304
00:17:12,880 --> 00:17:14,640
extremely generous treatment.

305
00:17:15,640 --> 00:17:16,240
Is that guaranteed?

306
00:17:20,160 --> 00:17:21,040
It's in black and white.

307
00:17:59,760 --> 00:18:01,600
He will never sign this contract.

308
00:18:09,720 --> 00:18:10,440
Xu Xinglang.

309
00:18:11,320 --> 00:18:12,360
Don't be so willful.

310
00:18:18,760 --> 00:18:19,360
Why won't you

311
00:18:19,360 --> 00:18:20,560
give us a chance?

312
00:18:21,000 --> 00:18:22,560
Jian Mo never did that thing.

313
00:18:22,760 --> 00:18:24,000
The truth will come out sooner or later.

314
00:18:25,160 --> 00:18:26,200
The company only cares about

315
00:18:26,200 --> 00:18:26,800
profit.

316
00:18:27,520 --> 00:18:29,200
The company only cares about profit.

317
00:18:30,880 --> 00:18:31,800
But this time,

318
00:18:32,640 --> 00:18:34,000
I hope you'll think long-term.

319
00:18:35,840 --> 00:18:36,320
Let's go.

320
00:18:38,480 --> 00:18:39,760
I hope later on

321
00:18:40,120 --> 00:18:42,040
you'll think this choice was worth it.

322
00:18:47,200 --> 00:18:47,840
Xinglang.

323
00:18:53,280 --> 00:18:54,040
The boss won't

324
00:18:54,800 --> 00:18:55,920
back down easily this time.

325
00:18:56,520 --> 00:18:57,080
What about you?

326
00:18:58,040 --> 00:18:59,160
Will you back down easily?

327
00:19:00,560 --> 00:19:01,720
Your mind's made up, huh?

328
00:19:03,680 --> 00:19:04,480
It is.

329
00:19:05,920 --> 00:19:07,280
Then leave this to me.

330
00:19:07,840 --> 00:19:09,000
I'll negotiate with the company.

331
00:19:19,320 --> 00:19:20,520
Thinking you're so cool again.

332
00:19:24,360 --> 00:19:24,960
From now on,

333
00:19:26,160 --> 00:19:27,200
don't do anything stupid.

334
00:19:28,880 --> 00:19:29,480
Let's go.

335
00:19:41,440 --> 00:19:42,240
You're leaving?

336
00:19:43,680 --> 00:19:44,640
We're heading out first.

337
00:19:44,680 --> 00:19:45,680
Sister Li called a halt to production.

338
00:19:46,040 --> 00:19:47,360
So we're all going home.

339
00:19:47,960 --> 00:19:48,880
We'll wait for further notice.

340
00:19:50,600 --> 00:19:51,080
Thanks for your hard work.

341
00:19:51,520 --> 00:19:52,160
Director Jian.

342
00:19:52,760 --> 00:19:54,240
We all believe in you.

343
00:19:54,760 --> 00:19:55,400
Thank you.

344
00:20:06,560 --> 00:20:07,400
What's going on?

345
00:20:08,040 --> 00:20:08,880
Production has stopped.

346
00:20:09,280 --> 00:20:10,560
Most likely, we won't film anymore.

347
00:20:11,280 --> 00:20:12,440
Sister Li is dismissing everyone.

348
00:20:12,640 --> 00:20:14,040
Settle what needs settling, leave what needs leaving.

349
00:20:14,120 --> 00:20:15,720
She's afraid the longer it drags on, the more she'll have to compensate.

350
00:20:17,320 --> 00:20:18,400
It's just over like this?

351
00:20:19,440 --> 00:20:19,880
Yes.

352
00:20:19,880 --> 00:20:21,040
You know what the public opinion is like right now.

353
00:20:21,160 --> 00:20:22,560
The platforms, the investors.

354
00:20:22,800 --> 00:20:23,880
They're blocking us at every level.

355
00:20:24,040 --> 00:20:25,120
She's been forced into this.

356
00:20:25,680 --> 00:20:26,840
Can you still hold on?

357
00:20:29,920 --> 00:20:30,760
I can.

358
00:20:31,600 --> 00:20:33,200
I'll go talk to Sister Li again.

359
00:20:33,880 --> 00:20:34,920
Go back and rest first.

360
00:20:35,160 --> 00:20:37,040
It won't look good if someone takes pictures of you.

361
00:21:05,480 --> 00:21:07,080
Sister Li, I'm sorry.

362
00:21:07,480 --> 00:21:09,080
I'm voluntarily leaving the crew.

363
00:21:09,320 --> 00:21:10,920
For the losses I've caused the crew.

364
00:21:11,080 --> 00:21:12,680
I'll find a way to compensate.

365
00:21:29,800 --> 00:21:30,640
Director.

366
00:21:31,240 --> 00:21:32,320
Come in.

367
00:21:38,360 --> 00:21:40,240
The investors have pulled out, you know that, right?

368
00:21:42,240 --> 00:21:43,640
I saw.

369
00:21:44,200 --> 00:21:45,840
All the crew members have left too.

370
00:21:49,400 --> 00:21:52,480
I'm here to discuss something with you.

371
00:21:54,120 --> 00:21:55,360
Stay.

372
00:21:55,920 --> 00:21:57,160
Keep filming.

373
00:21:58,320 --> 00:21:59,560
How can we keep going?

374
00:22:01,720 --> 00:22:03,640
I borrowed some money myself.

375
00:22:04,560 --> 00:22:06,040
Xinglang also put in some money.

376
00:22:07,120 --> 00:22:08,720
It's enough for us to finish filming.

377
00:22:09,080 --> 00:22:11,560
We don't expect chances from the outside world.

378
00:22:12,040 --> 00:22:15,320
We can finish the film on our own.

379
00:22:16,160 --> 00:22:18,360
But the public opinion is still out there.

380
00:22:19,240 --> 00:22:20,640
Even if we finish it.

381
00:22:22,280 --> 00:22:23,720
Will the film ever be released?

382
00:22:26,440 --> 00:22:27,600
I don't know.

383
00:22:28,560 --> 00:22:31,000
But at least we can finish filming it.

384
00:22:31,560 --> 00:22:33,880
Only then will we be qualified to talk about anything else.

385
00:22:36,040 --> 00:22:37,040
Jian Mo.

386
00:22:38,640 --> 00:22:40,760
Let's not back down, okay?

387
00:22:41,480 --> 00:22:42,680
No matter how hard it gets.

388
00:22:42,840 --> 00:22:44,560
We'll find a way out.

389
00:22:44,920 --> 00:22:45,680
Won't we?

390
00:22:49,200 --> 00:22:50,040
Director Du.

391
00:22:52,800 --> 00:22:55,080
I'm willing to give up all my salary.

392
00:22:55,520 --> 00:22:57,720
Let's finish this film properly.

393
00:22:59,520 --> 00:23:00,520
Absolutely not.

394
00:23:01,400 --> 00:23:02,720
I'm an investor now too.

395
00:23:02,720 --> 00:23:04,080
I still have to pay you.

396
00:23:05,160 --> 00:23:05,960
Xinglang.

397
00:23:06,200 --> 00:23:08,120
You can be such a CEO sometimes.

398
00:23:11,320 --> 00:23:12,640
That won't do.

399
00:23:13,400 --> 00:23:14,800
This whole thing started because of me.

400
00:23:15,840 --> 00:23:16,800
With your help.

401
00:23:16,800 --> 00:23:18,080
I'm already very grateful.

402
00:23:18,280 --> 00:23:19,280
Alright, alright.

403
00:23:19,840 --> 00:23:21,320
I won't make you feel any more guilty.

404
00:23:21,880 --> 00:23:22,560
Don't worry.

405
00:23:23,200 --> 00:23:24,120
I had someone calculate it.

406
00:23:24,280 --> 00:23:25,440
This film will definitely be a huge hit.

407
00:23:25,720 --> 00:23:26,720
That's why I invested.

408
00:23:30,000 --> 00:23:31,400
Lighting guys, get the lights up now!

409
00:23:32,960 --> 00:23:33,560
Director Du said.

410
00:23:34,160 --> 00:23:35,200
The latest script has been revised.

411
00:23:35,480 --> 00:23:36,640
Let's finish filming it.

412
00:23:38,120 --> 00:23:38,600
Okay.

413
00:23:41,680 --> 00:23:42,600
All departments, stand by.

414
00:23:43,800 --> 00:23:44,560
Received, received.

415
00:23:45,600 --> 00:23:46,360
Action.

416
00:23:50,280 --> 00:23:51,560
I've been looking for you for a long time.

417
00:23:55,720 --> 00:23:56,640
Do you really have to go?

418
00:23:57,480 --> 00:23:59,800
Staying here won't do either of us any good.

419
00:24:01,240 --> 00:24:02,280
The mission failed.

420
00:24:05,040 --> 00:24:06,840
I still have many missions to complete.

421
00:24:10,240 --> 00:24:11,240
Stay with me, please.

422
00:24:12,560 --> 00:24:13,480
Before.

423
00:24:14,440 --> 00:24:15,960
I didn't know how to love someone.

424
00:24:16,720 --> 00:24:18,600
I could only love you in my own way.

425
00:24:18,960 --> 00:24:19,800
But I ended up hurting you.

426
00:24:21,920 --> 00:24:23,200
Can you give me another chance?

427
00:24:24,240 --> 00:24:25,080
Be with me.

428
00:24:27,760 --> 00:24:29,080
You'll face a lot of danger.

429
00:24:29,960 --> 00:24:31,200
Including your whole life.

430
00:24:33,000 --> 00:24:34,320
It will spiral out of control because of me.

431
00:24:36,360 --> 00:24:38,200
You taught me how to love.

432
00:24:40,240 --> 00:24:41,080
Love is bravery.

433
00:24:42,200 --> 00:24:42,880
It is trust.

434
00:24:43,840 --> 00:24:45,240
It is fearing no hardship.

435
00:24:47,720 --> 00:24:48,840
I want to be with you.

436
00:24:50,880 --> 00:24:51,480
I love you.

437
00:24:52,680 --> 00:24:54,000
Will you be with me?

438
00:24:57,280 --> 00:24:58,160
Will you?

439
00:25:08,240 --> 00:25:08,960
I will.
